room_title: Escape room "Super Villains" by Escape Room Arlington in Arlington (VA)
room_address: 2301 Columbia Pike Suite C Arlington, VA 22204
room_description: Slip on your spandex and strap on your utility belt! The super villains have escaped the comics! Using your wit and wiles, you must break into the very heart of darkness; transport yourself into the comic lairs of four of the city's most notorious super villains, discover the clues they've left behind and save the city... if it's not too late.
